N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4212.5 - Registration of stable employees

State Regulations

The personnel of every stable and changes thereof shall
be registered by horsemen with the association on whose tracks their horses are
racing or stabled and shall be available at all times to representatives of the
commission. Notes
